<colspec colnum = "2" colname = "2" colwidth = "5.015in"/>
<tbody>
<row rowsep = "1">
<entry colname = "1" border-top = "1" border-bottom = "1" border-left = "1" border-right = "0" align = "right">
<ptxt>
<symbol name = "MANOTE" width = "5.132mm" height = "3.048mm"/>
 1: 
</ptxt>
</entry>
<entry colname = "2" border-top = "1" border-bottom = "1" border-left = "0" border-right = "1" align = "left">
<ptxt>
Ce symbole indique que le panneau arrière et le panneau extérieur de logement de feu arrière sont remplacés en même temps. 
</ptxt>
</entry>
</row>
<row rowsep = "0">
